        public CCinemaTicket(java.lang.String name,
                     org.javamoney.moneta.Money price,
                     java.lang.Integer i_row,
                     java.lang.Integer i_seat,
                     java.lang.Long eventID,
                     java.lang.String roomName,
                     java.lang.String startTime,
                     CSeat.Etype seatType,
                     java.lang.String moviename)
        Creates a new CCinemaTicket
        Parameters:
        name - String : name of move for purchases, reservation ID for reservations, 000 for canceled or timed out reservations,
        price - Money : Money value of the final price
        i_row - Integer: seat's row number
        i_seat - Integer: seat's seat number
        eventID - Long : corresponding event ID
        roomName - String name of the room the corresponding event is in
        startTime - String start time of the event saved as string
        seatType - Etype type of the ticket's seat, loge or pit
        moviename - String name of the movie
